{"tid":2270874,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"律政司不會就南丫海難再向任何人提出檢控","createTime":"2020-11-04T09:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T10:17:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c61e23bf0e39e9a6debfb7aeba559482b0ef5679","tid":2270874,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:04:15.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】律政司決定不會就2012年的南丫海難，再向任何人或公司提出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n當局書面回覆立法會質詢時指，警方分別在2015年及2018年，先後就南丫海難，向律政司提交對海事處以外人員及機構的調查報告及相關證據。<br />\n<br />\n警方上月中接獲律政司通知，決定不會再檢控任何人或公司。而警方2015年，已向死因庭提交39份死因調查報告，並在上月中，將所有調查結果及法律意見通知死因裁判官。<br />\n<br />\n律政司強調，若案件有合理定罪機會及符合公眾利益，才會提控；早前已就本案，先後向兩艘船的船長及兩名海事處人員提出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=411621\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411621&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=df251f74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411621&h=e118e7b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=411621</a>"},{"pid":"1849f515c133384067a9983b1d958f4461f746fe","tid":2270874,"uid":107577,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"我話冇事就冇事<br />\n你死你事"},{"pid":"189c6af1a5b23782784f5ce886721f72eccdee36","tid":2270874,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12a63b3642261e4e2a72816a76369ecf9d9982e","tid":2270874,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"......"},{"pid":"4d2a863aa3f8f8742b2f1df2e187224a2ef51b18","tid":2270874,"uid":58880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:09: